sentences.content: Scene narratives lets the user describe complex scenes by decomposing it into simpler subscenes.
The hair salon is named Ann's.
The storefront has large glass windows.
The door is red with a welcome mat.
A man is going to the hair salon.
He is wearing a yellow shirt and jeans.
He is stepping onto the sidewalk from the street.
The hair stylist is wearing a yellow dress.
She is currently cutting a client's hair.
Her client is a woman with long hair.
The woman is sitting in a salon chair.
A man is waiting in the next room.
He is wearing an orange shirt.
He is reading a magazine.
